Package: balancR
Type: Package
Title: Data Balancing and Scaling Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Milos", family = "Simovic", email = "milos.simovic@botany.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")), person(given = "Sean", family = "Michaletz", email = "sean.michaletz@ubc.ca", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides tools for balancing imbalanced data in scaling analyses using
    bootstrapping, and for comparing regression coefficients (slopes and intercepts)
    between original and balanced samples. Please cite Simovic and Michaletz (2025) 
    when using this package (https://doi.org/10.1111/geb.70019).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    ggExtra,
    ggpmisc,
    gridExtra,
    rlang,
    grid,
    smatr
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/MSimovic21/balancR
BugReports: https://github.com/MSimovic21/balancR/issues
